    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant. This high-revving unit utilizes six individual throttle bodies to deliver a crisp, linear throttle response, paired with a tactile Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains sharp, benefiting from documented subframe reinforcement and a recently serviced VANOS system to ensure long-term mechanical integrity. Power is managed effectively through the factory M Variable Differential Lock, providing excellent lateral grip and exit speeds. While the exterior shows minor age-appropriate patina, the mechanical components are robust, and the suspension geometry remains true, offering the precise feedback expected of a well-maintained M-car.",
